    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Sweep-Display dialog-box</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Use the </text><text styleclass="VariableName-IT" translate="true">Sweep-Display dialog-box</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> to read the exact motion-values of each motion-derivative (P,V,A,J) as a function of the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Cursor-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> parameter. The Cursor-Position specifies the exact location of a cursor on the X-axis of the motion graphs.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">The </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">Sweep Display</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> evaluates the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">EXACT</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> values of the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">PVAJ motion-derivatives</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> at the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">X-axis</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> value as defined by the </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Cursor-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">. </text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">The </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-Master-Machine-Angle" styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Master Machine Angle</link><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> is synchronized with the Cursor-Position</text></para>
