            <li styleclass="HowTo Bulleted"><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true">Maximum </text><text styleclass="Interface2" translate="true">Cursor Position</text><text styleclass="HowTo Bulleted" translate="true"> =  Motion-Width – (Number of Steps / Motion-Width).</text></li>
